It is 3 km due S. of the actual site of Aguilani (which is misplaced on maps) and 13.5 km N. of Choquetanga. High, virgin cloud forests, quite diverse with Brunnelia, Clusia, Vallea, Podocarpus, Clethra, Weinmannia and Hesperomeles all common. Collections made in the turfy areas around the lake.
